---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import sustainabilityLogo from "../../assets/images/sustainability_logo.svg";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sustainability">
  <div class="w-full container mx-auto px-8 py-12">
    <div class="flex justify-left">
      <nav class="text-sm sm:text-base pb-6">
        <ol class="list-none p-0 inline-flex space-x-2">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              onclick="window.location.href='/';"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              height="1em"
              viewBox="0 0 576 512"
              class="cursor-pointer hover:fill-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300 mr-2"
              fill="#4b5563"
              ><!--! Font Awesome Free 6.4.2 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. -->
              <path
                d="M575.8 255.5c0 18-15 32.1-32 32.1h-32l.7 160.2c0 2.7-.2 5.4-.5 8.1V472c0 22.1-17.9 40-40 40H456c-1.1 0-2.2 0-3.3-.1c-1.4 .1-2.8 .1-4.2 .1H416 392c-22.1 0-40-17.9-40-40V448 384c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32H256c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32v64 24c0 22.1-17.9 40-40 40H160 128.1c-1.5 0-3-.1-4.5-.2c-1.2 .1-2.4 .2-3.6 .2H104c-22.1 0-40-17.9-40-40V360c0-.9 0-1.9 .1-2.8V287.6H32c-18 0-32-14-32-32.1c0-9 3-17 10-24L266.4 8c7-7 15-8 22-8s15 2 21 7L564.8 231.5c8 7 12 15 11 24z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <a
              href="/about"
              class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300"
              >About</a
            >
            <span class="mx-2">/</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="text-yellow-600 font-semibold">Sustainability</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight pb-4">Sustainability</h1>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 items-start gap-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 prose">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Our Approach to Sustainability</h2>
          <p>
            We know construction and joinery work can have an impact on the
            environment — and we don’t take that lightly. That’s why we aim to
            reduce waste, reuse materials where possible, and make thoughtful
            choices every day on site.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">
            Staying Within the Rules (and Going Beyond)
          </h2>
          <p>
            We meet all the environmental regulations that apply to our work.
            But we don’t just stop at the minimum. Where there isn’t a law or
            guideline in place, we use common sense and experience to do what’s
            right for the environment — and we keep a record of it.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Getting the Team Involved</h2>
          <p>
            Everyone we work with is part of this. We make sure our team
            understands the importance of working cleanly and efficiently — and
            we back that up with training, site discussions, and regular reviews
            of how we work.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Looking After People Too</h2>
          <p>
            Sustainability isn't just about the environment — it’s about people
            too. We actively promote wellbeing, health, and safety for our
            clients, team, and community through how we work and the choices we
            make.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you'd like more detail or a written policy, just
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="font-semibold text-blue-700 hover:underline"
              >get in touch</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <Image
          src={sustainabilityLogo}
          width="526"
          height="489"
          class="object-fit max-w-full h-auto mx-auto block mb-4"
          alt="Sustainability"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
